market_context: U.S. stock futures are indicating a positive open following strong earnings reports from major tech companies and a rebound in Asian markets overnight. Investors are also anticipating the release of key economic data, including the latest GDP growth figures and consumer confidence index, which are expected to show continued economic resilience.
